channel.title: What is the difference between these two types of pictures?
channel.description:
Ok first off i would just like to thank you for taking the time to help, it means a lot to me!
I am not new to private servers (ive been playing them for like a year) but i have decided to try to start my own private server. I have downloaded several sources but am still unsure as to which one i should use.
What is the difference between these two types of sources?
IS one a 317 and the other a 377 or what?
[img]http://i425.photobucket.com/albums/pp340/adinofaries/pic2.jpg[/img]
and heres the other
[img]http://i425.photobucket.com/albums/pp340/adinofaries/pic1.jpg[/img]
If these both are bad please tell me of one that you would suggest using, thanks in advance,
Sincerely, Adin
